I/O structure 151 4.5 I/O features I/O features (adapters) include ports6 to connect the IBM z16 A02 and IBM z16 AGZ to external devices, networks, or other zSystems. I/O features are plugged into the PCIe+ I/O drawer, based on the machine’s configuration rules. Different types of I/O cards are available, one for each channel or link type.
